1505  struct Status : Bitfield<Status>
1506  {
1507  enum _enumType : uint8_t
1508  {
1509  NONE = 0x00,
1510  ACTIVE = 0x01,
1511  ENABLED = 0x02,
1512  TEST = 0x04,
1513  ALL = 0x07,
1514  };
1515  uint8_t value = NONE;
1516 
1517  Status() : value(NONE) {}
1518  Status(int val) : value((uint8_t)val) {}
1519  operator uint8_t() const { return value; }
1520  Status& operator=(uint8_t val) { value = val; return *this; }
1521  Status& operator=(int val) { value = val; return *this; }
1522  Status& operator|=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value | val; }
1523  Status& operator&=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value & val; }
1524 
1525  bool active() const { return (value & ACTIVE) > 0; }
1526  void active(bool val) { if(val) value |= ACTIVE; else value &= ~ACTIVE; }
1527  bool enabled() const { return (value & ENABLED) > 0; }
1528  void enabled(bool val) { if(val) value |= ENABLED; else value &= ~ENABLED; }
1529  bool test() const { return (value & TEST) > 0; }
1530  void test(bool val) { if(val) value |= TEST; else value &= ~TEST; }
1531 
1532  bool allSet() const { return value == ALL; }
1533  void setAll() { value |= ALL; }
1534  };
